name: Genshin Impact: Villain Life Simulator
summary: Upon entering the world of Genshin Impact, Lucas unexpectedly activates the Villain Simulator, forcing him to take on the role of a major antagonist in a simulated reality. His missions include:Bullying Keqing at schoolBlackmailing Shenhe into carrying out various tasksRaising an army of undead to destroy MondstadtAnd much more...To balance the evil acts committed in the simulation, Lucas must earn good karma by acting virtuously in the real world. However, he never imagined that one day, Shenhe, wielding a spear, would confront him in reality:Lucas, you have committed countless evil deeds. Today, I will kill you to uphold justice!Lucas: ...Wait, werent those just fake simulations?
author: _Nia
